OL,3,CFamilies affected by baby loss come
OL,4,Ctogether to find comfort
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey took part in a
OL,7,Fstarlight walk this weekend to mark
OL,8,FBaby Loss Awareness Week.
OL,10,FHosted by baby loss and safer
OL,11,Fpregnancy charity Philip's Footprints,
OL,12,Fthe aim was to spark conversation
OL,13,Faround child bereavement and give
OL,14,Ffamilies a chance to feel less alone
OL,15,Fwith their grief.
OL,17,FThe charity donates memory boxes to
OL,18,Ffamilies experiencing the loss of a
OL,19,Fchild in Jersey - giving them an
OL,20,Fopportunity to create tangible
OL,21,Fmemories and keepsakes.
