OL,3,CFamilies affected by baby loss come
OL,4,Ctogether to find comfort
OL,6,FLauren Lynda Callaghan says the
OL,7,Fcharity's support was invaluable in
OL,8,Fhelping her navigate the painful
OL,9,Fexperience of losing a baby, after her
OL,10,Fdaughter was born sleeping at 21 weeks
OL,11,Fin May last year.
OL,13,FShe says its a period of time she
OL,14,Fremembers as being "an absolute blur".
OL,16,F"It's not until you're in it that you
OL,17,Funderstand the emotions connected to
OL,18,Fit, which are incredibly raw", she
OL,19,Fadds.
