OL,3,CFamilies affected by baby loss come
OL,4,Ctogether to find comfort
OL,6,FAfter realising she needed to seek
OL,7,Fsupport, Lauren turned to the
OL,8,Fmaternity unit and was put in touch
OL,9,Fwith Karina Ward - a bereavement
OL,10,Fcounsellor funded by Philip's
OL,11,FFootsteps at the Enid Quenault Health
OL,12,Fand Wellbeing Centre.
OL,14,FLauren says the service provided her
OL,15,Fwith the safe space she needed.
OL,17,F"It feels like it's my room, it's my
OL,18,Fdaughter's room", she explains.
