OL,6,F"I come in here and I automatically
OL,7,Ffeel calm and have the space to
OL,8,Fnavigate through the emotions with the
OL,9,Fcounsellor."
OL,11,FKarina says that for family and
OL,12,Ffriends, it can be difficult to
OL,13,Fdetermine how to support someone who
OL,14,Fis going through the emotional
OL,15,Fexperience.
