OL,3,CFamilies affected by baby loss come
OL,4,Ctogether to find comfort
OL,6,F"It has to be led by the person who
OL,7,Fhas gone through the loss - sometimes
OL,8,Fit can be offering some practical
OL,9,Fhelp, such as if they need cooking
OL,10,Fdone for them, which might be the last
OL,11,Fthing on their mind", she explains.
OL,13,FShe adds that "everyone who goes
OL,14,Fthrough a loss deserves to be held",
OL,15,Fand this is what she aims to achieve
OL,16,Fwith her work.
