OL,3,CFamilies affected by baby loss come
OL,4,Ctogether to find comfort
OL,6,FKenan Osborne, the charity's chair,
OL,7,Fsays the memory boxes donated by the
OL,8,Fcharity - filled with items such as
OL,9,Fkeepsakes, a photo album, and
OL,10,Fchildren's books to help bereaved
OL,11,Fsiblings navigate their feelings - are
OL,12,Fdesigned to reinforce the support
OL,13,Foffered by counselling.
OL,15,F"The boxes are designed for people to
OL,16,Ffind ways to remember their loved
OL,17,Fones", he explains.
