OL,3,CFamilies affected by baby loss come
OL,4,Ctogether to find comfort
OL,6,FThe charity also offers group sessions
OL,7,Ffor those who wish to talk about their
OL,8,Floss journey and points families
OL,9,Ftowards other services that can help.
OL,11,FWithout the counselling and support
OL,12,Fshe received from Philip's Footprints,
OL,13,FLauren says she doesn't know where she
OL,14,Fwould be in her grief journey.
OL,16,F"You feel like the only person going
OL,17,Fthrough it at the time" she explains
OL,18,F"having someone to talk to and a room
OL,19,Fto support me through those really raw
OL,20,Femotions was unbelievable.
